md-artefacts
============

Plain-text boot/failure proof logs for the sun4v MD/hv-config emulation test
matrix in https://unix0cc.github.io/md/

Each PASS/FAIL cell in the matrix links here directly:

    https://unix0cc.github.io/md-artefacts/<build-slug>__<os-slug>.txt


Naming convention
-----------------
    <build-slug>__<os-slug>.txt

The matrix row (MD/hv build) and column (guest OS image), joined by a double
underscore. For example, the "Solaris 11 11/11 text" column of the tlb_fix/2048
row is:

    tlb_fix-2048__sol-11-1111-text.txt

A third "__" component marks a variant run of the same cell, e.g.
tlb_fix-2048__snv_134-ai-iso__pagesize-mask-suppressed.txt


Publishing
----------
GitHub Pages, source: main branch, / (root). Any .txt file added here becomes
reachable at https://unix0cc.github.io/md-artefacts/<file> once Pages finishes
building.
